	<div style="text-align:right;">
		TYSKI, Ronaldo Gustavo Albini<sup>1</sup>; OLIVEIRA, Luísa Bordignon Félix de<sup>2</sup>; BRANCO, Melina<sup>3</sup>; SAMPAIO, Claudia Paraguacu Pupo<sup>4</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
		<I>--</I>
